      "message": "Comparing configs is basically the same as comparing backend format and color type combos. However, the color type on this level is only really used for getting a swizzle.\n\nThis is valid cause all we are asking is can I copy this proxy into another. Our copySurface is already defined to ignore origin and swizzle while copying (that is the responsibility of calling code to handle if they care). So the only real check we need is that their backend formats are the same.",
